---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'May 2026';
---

<Layout
  title="Now — Juan Iznardo"
  description="What Juan Iznardo is currently working on and focused on."
>
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <!-- Back link -->
    <a
      href="/"
      class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-mono text-xs text-[var(--color-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-accent)] transition-colors duration-[var(--duration-fast)] mb-12 group"
    >
      <span class="group-hover:-translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-[var(--duration-fast)]">←</span>
      home
    </a>

    <header class="mb-10">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <span class="font-mono text-xs text-[var(--color-muted)] uppercase tracking-widest">
          /now — updated {lastUpdated}
        </span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="font-mono text-3xl font-medium">What I'm doing now</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="border-t border-[var(--color-border)] mb-10"></div>

    <div class="space-y-10 text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed">
      <section>
        <h2 class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-[var(--color-accent)] mb-3">
          building
        </h2>
        <p>
          A Game Boy emulator in C. Primarily a learning project — the goal is to understand how
          a real CPU executes instructions, how memory is mapped, and how the PPU renders pixels.
          Currently working through the Sharp LR35902 instruction set.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-[var(--color-accent)] mb-3">
          learning
        </h2>
        <p>
          Web scraping with Python — building the skills to offer this as a service.
          Also deepening my C knowledge through the emulator work.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-[var(--color-accent)] mb-3">
          finishing
        </h2>
        <p>
          Final year of my Computer Engineering degree in Spain. Thinking about what comes next.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-[var(--color-accent)] mb-3">
          reading
        </h2>
        <p>
          Susskind's <em>The Theoretical Minimum</em> series. Theoretical physics as an honest
          hobby — I find it more interesting than I am good at it.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>

    <div class="border-t border-[var(--color-border)] mt-12 pt-8">
      <p class="font-mono text-xs text-[var(--color-muted)] opacity-50">
        Inspired by <a href="https://nownownow.com/about" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:text-[var(--color-accent)] transition-colors">/now pages</a>.
        This page reflects what's true at the time of writing, not a permanent statement.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
